title: Top Floor Corner Unit for 8/1, Updated Bathroom, HW Floors
posting_body: ['Second Floor Unit for August 1 in Brownstone at Lexington & Grand Avenue, Hardwood Floors & High Ceilings, Updated Bathroom', 'Property Address', '45 Lexington Pkwy.', '- #11 | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: 08/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'With occupied units, we are only able to do a showing after an application is approved.', ' To apply, each adult would go to <URL> and upload last two pay statements and/or proof of other income.', 'Second floor apartment available August 1 in St. Paul brownstone.', 'Hardwood floors throughout with high ceilings and lots of windows.', 'Living room has a large storage closet.', ' The bedroom has a good sized closet, ceiling fan and connects to the full bathroom.', 'The full bathroom has a tiled floor, pedestal sink and clawfoot tub.', 'Prime St. Paul location at the intersection of Lexington & Grand Avenue.', 'Just across the street from Starbucks, The Uptowner Cafe and The Lexington.', "Walking distance to Cafe Latte, Bruegger's Bagels, Chipotle, Brassa and many other shops, bars and restaurants.", 'Unlimited laundry on-site for $12/month.', "There's a short wait list for an off-street parking space available for $75/month.", 'Cats are okay with a $35/month pet fee per.', 'Sorry no dogs.', '$50 application fee per adult', 'We check income (gross household income must be at least 3 times rent), credit (must be 600+), criminal and rental history', 'Rent includes water/sewer, trash and gas heat', 'Renters are responsible for electric and cooking gas', 'Call Dakota at', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a showing', 'Agent: Dakota DeHaven', 'BROKER: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 680', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $949.00', 'Available: 08/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $949.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
